  "title_extended": "MikroTik CRS112-8P-4S-IN Switch – 8x PoE, 4x SFP",
  "short_description": "8x Gbit PoE 802.3af/at, 4xSFP Cage, RouterOS L5",
  "description": "8x Gbit PoE 802.3af/at, 4xSFP Cage, RouterOS L5",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Combining Router & Switch Functionality",
      "text": "Introducing the MikroTik CRS112-8P-4S-IN, a high-powered networking solution. The CRS series, including the CRS112-8P-4S-IN, is driven by RouterOS, merging the capabilities of a fully functional router with those of a manageable switch enhanced with Layer 3 (L3) features. Within its interface, all the specific Switch configuration options are readily accessible through a dedicated Switch menu."
    },
    {
      "heading": "High-Powered Connectivity",
      "text": "The CRS112-8P-4S-IN features eight Gigabit Ethernet ports, each equipped with Power-over-Ethernet (PoE) capabilities. These ports offer the convenience of various power output options, including autosensing 802.3af/at PoE/PoE+ and Passive PoE. Additionally, it boasts four SFP (Small Form-Factor Pluggable) ports, providing versatile optical fiber connectivity options, and supporting uplinks with speeds of up to 1 Gbps. This array of ports ensures your network remains adaptable and ready to meet evolving needs."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Advanced Networking Features",
      "text": "The MikroTik CRS112-8P-4S-IN offers a host of advanced networking features that boost your network's performance and security. It ensures smooth data flow with non-blocking Layer 2 switching capacity, as well as efficient routing via a 16K host table. You can handle up to 4,000 VLANs simultaneously with IEEE 802.1Q VLAN support, and enhance security through port isolation, port security, and broadcast storm control."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Power Supply Options",
      "text": "The CRS112-8P-4S-IN features a secondary DC jack on the back of the enclosure, which supports a 48-57 V power supply (not included but available for purchase separately). When connected to 48-57 V DC input, the CRS112-8P-4S-IN can power 802.3af/at devices, automatically detecting and providing the correct power to devices."
    }
  ],
